---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Materials"
  description="Stone material information for marble, granite, travertine and more."
>
  <section class="materials-overview">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span>Materials</span>
      </nav>

      <h1>Materials</h1>
      <p>Learn about the stone materials we work with and how to choose the right option for your project.</p>

      <div class="materials-notice">
        <p>这里可以作为材料百科入口，将来可通过 <code>src/content/materials</code> 来管理每种石材内容。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.materials-overview {
  padding: 80px 0;
}
.materials-notice {
  margin-top: 40px;
  padding: 24px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  background: rgba(0,0,0,.03);
}
</style>
